_sText:
**fy _ poolparty _ destroyed**
==================
I spotted alot of poolparty version's, so I thought now it's time for my version. The layout is basicly the same but I added a lot more detail into the map, also a 3d skybox and HDR.I gave the map a deserted edge to it.
 Enjoy and have fun !

**Features**
==================
- Alot of detail 
- HDR
- Soundscape
-  **OPTIMISATION** 
- Animated Water Caustics 

Installation
==================
To download this map simply join my server which has this map running 24/7 atm click **[here](steam://connect/82.74.11.188:27015">82.74.11.188:27015 "here")**, and start playing right away!

Or download and unpack the .rar file to:

"Steam\steamapps\USERNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps"

Comment & Rate
==================  
Please add a comment and rate on my map.
Also tell me if you see any bugs. I'll try to fix them.
